  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"dSAae6LB\">会的呀，全程<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=747182520&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=M%E5%AD%97%E8%85%BF&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">M字腿<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，或者分开，因为里面还在肿胀，会有明显的牵拉感，走路需要扶着走，或者坐轮椅</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-38e4d5c68c31cd76359aa710a0694915_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1170\" data-rawheight=\"1534\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-6b86c17a125f8799a1f7788c2f264373\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1170\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-38e4d5c68c31cd76359aa710a0694915_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-38e4d5c68c31cd76359aa710a0694915_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1170\" data-rawheight=\"1534\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-6b86c17a125f8799a1f7788c2f264373\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1170\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-38e4d5c68c31cd76359aa710a0694915_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-38e4d5c68c31cd76359aa710a0694915_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"1534\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"69C2PiSS\">其次是，长期的通模具，导致里面的伤口一直比较难愈合，导致肿胀，所以不建议长期走路</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f783118b886fa1599026506216651b09_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1170\" data-rawheight=\"1542\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-4f9b7029d2e43de09333bd317553da55\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1170\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f783118b886fa1599026506216651b09_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1170' height='1542'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1170\" data-rawheight=\"1542\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-4f9b7029d2e43de09333bd317553da55\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1170\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f783118b886fa1599026506216651b09_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f783118b886fa1599026506216651b09_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div><figcaption>通模具</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"Clxqy_wV\">但是，一直不走路，又会容易导致，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=747182520&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%A1%80%E6%A0%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">血栓<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>根血液不循环，所以只能一边痛一边走啦。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
